Scum of the earth actually...in fact I cannot wait until I here him begging for another CR so I can laugh in his face, or even better drag his dead body DEEPER into the dungeon.<br>
<br>
At level 19 he promised me and a guy I was grouping with 100 plat to go help him get his body back in 'Lavastorm'.  I figured he's super tough and just wanted Bard Speed to get there or something, I dunno...he was red to me and anon (didn't even have his tag up) so I figured what the heck.<br>
<br>
Run him to Lavastorm with a bit of a hassel, was in HHP grindin off orcs.  Get to lavastorm, do a quick locate on him...no corpses in the zone.<br>
<br>
&quot;Oh its in that dungeon here.&quot;<br>
<br>
(The one that you forgot to mention when you invited me to come along...the one that you know everything in there cons RED to my 19 butt?...shoulda cut my losses, but he seemed rather helpless and what can I say, I like adventure...he promises MORE money if I'd stay and help him)<br>
<br>
Now he starts to come forward with a twisted version of the truth...&quot;its at the Sol B zone...the one that is not that far in...&quot;<br>
<br>
Ok, screw it, I know casters see invis, but what the hell, I'm the wicked tough bard, I'll go in drag him, and get the cash.<br>
