Fuckin Sand-Shitter...shit speaker...<br>
<br>
He's not at the close Sol B zone...nothing there...start enlisting help thinking this guy is a moron but at that point even more determined to be somewhat decent to him...I ask him for recollections of his fight, enlist the aid of a rogue and a cleric to help out...all sorts of shit, 2 hours later we get his body and get him raised...(Thanks Cards and Qwenu...)<br>
