&quot;Sorry lets run to FP I don't have the money on me...&quot;<br>
<br>
Ok, what the hell, on the way back he decides to aggro and kill all the halflings...luckily I got far enough away that my speedsong didn't trip on him and thereby lose me a bunch of faction with the lil peoples...I think he pulled this to try and get us to disband...25 minutes later he finally zones into WC...<br>
<br>
&quot;Sorry I was having too much fun&quot;<br>
<br>
Qnewu, Cards and I in tells knowing just knowing that he's probably going to rip us off...but thinking what the heck we'll stick it out.<br>
<br>
Zone to FP, he says, whats the quickest way back to the moon?  Ummm, duh get to spires...maybe the ones in G Fay are closer if you catch the boat...<br>
<br>
We goto the bank, Cards follows him to the docks, where he LDs and disappears...<br>
<br>
Now if the Fucker had asked for help straight up and not offered any payment I would have gone anyway...Whimsy is just about chaotic enough to do that, and dying only means she gets to hear a new joke from Bristlebane anyway...but not only did he promise cash up front, he lied about the difficulty and then INTENTIONALLY tried to fuck over us with faction hits to get us to leave...Halflings don't 'aggro' on you accidentally...especially green ones...<br>
